title: Former CNN anchor Bobbie Battista dies of cancer at age 67
description: Bobbie Battista, who was among the original anchors for CNN Headline News and hosted CNN’s “TalkBack Live,” has died
content:
LOS ANGELES -- 
Bobbie Battista, who was among the original anchors for CNN Headline News and hosted CNNs TalkBack Live, has died. She was 67.
Battista died Tuesday after a four-year battle with cervical cancer, family spokeswoman Wendy Guarisco told CNN.
